<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>The College gives credit for courses in which Advanced Placement Exams have been given and in which appropriate levels of competence have been demonstrated. If a student has taken Advanced Placement courses in high school and the respective examination and receives a grade of 3 or higher on the exam, he/she can receive college credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.davidsonccc.edu/pdfs/catalog/ScholasticStandards.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

